---
title: Honey Mustard Rump Steak with Creamy Herb Potatoes & Garden Salad
description: Our chefs are always looking to take “meat and potatoes” to the next level. This week, they really raised the steaks (we’ll show
ourselves out). Tonight, sirloin is pan-seared with a tangy honey mustard glaze. On the side, there’s a creamy potato salad that'll have
you licking your lips and fingertips by the end of it. Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
